{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2020",
    "useDefineForClassFields": true,
    "lib": ["ES2020", "DOM", "DOM.Iterable"],
    "module": "ESNext",
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "moduleResolution": "bundler",
    "allowImportingTsExtensions": true,
    "jsx": "react-jsx",
    "strict": false,
    "noEmit": true,
    "noUnusedLocals": false,
    "noUnusedParameters": false,
    "noFallthroughCasesInSwitch": false
  },
  "include": ["src"]
}
```

AND also go to **`package.json`** on GitHub, click pencil, find the build script line and change it from:
```
"build": "tsc -b && vite build"
```

to:
```
"build": "vite build"
